@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### 0) health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 1) 테스트용 세션 생성
# @name createChatSession
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "E2E system prompt flow"
}

### 2) 생성된 세션 ID 확인
@chatSessionId = {{createChatSession.response.body.$.id}}

### 3) 현재 system prompt 조회 (v1 기본값)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/system-prompts/current

### 4) system prompt 업데이트 -> v2 생성
PUT {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/system-prompts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "You are a senior Python tutor. Answer in Korean."
}

### 5) system prompt 업데이트 -> v3 생성
PUT {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/system-prompts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "You are a strict reviewer. Keep answers short."
}

### 6) 이력 조회 (v3 current, v2/v1 history)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/system-prompts

### 7) v1을 current로 활성화
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/system-prompts/1/activate

### 8) 현재 system prompt 다시 조회 (v1인지 확인)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/system-prompts/current

### 9) 비현재 버전(v2) 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/system-prompts/2

### 10) 삭제 후 이력 조회 (v2 제거 확인)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/system-prompts

### 11) 현재 버전(v1) 삭제 시도 -> 400 기대
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}/system-prompts/1

### 12) 테스트 종료 후 세션 삭제(원하면 실행)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/chat-sessions/{{chatSessionId}}